      <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://simbatango.com/2009/09/23/homero-manzi-un-poeta-en-la-tormenta/manzi/&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://simbatango.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2009/09/manzi.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;manzi&#34; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;A &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.manzilapelicula.com.ar/&#34;&gt;new film&lt;/a&gt; about the tango poet &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.todotango.com/english/creadores/manzi.html&#34;&gt;Homero Manzi&lt;/a&gt; was just released in Argentina. Manzi is the author of famous tangos like &lt;em&gt;Malena&lt;/em&gt;, &lt;em&gt;Sur&lt;/em&gt; and &lt;em&gt;Barrio de tango&lt;/em&gt;. He worked with Troilo for several years, and in cooperation with Sebastián Piana, he revitalized the milonga genre with &lt;em&gt;Milonga sentimental&lt;/em&gt; in 1931.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The film is apparently a combination of archive material and reconstruction of scenes from his life. It will be interesting to watch, I will probably wait until it is available on dvd, hopefully it won&amp;rsquo;t take that long.&lt;/p&gt;

